search_results.title: Girish and the Chronicles
search_results.snippet: Girish and the Chronicles, also known simply as GATC, is an Indian rock band from India, Sikkim, formed in 2009, by vocalist Girish Pradhan.

search_results.title: Girish And The Chronicles
search_results.snippet: Acclaimed hard rockers Girish And The Chronicles have announced the upcoming release of a re-record of their debut album, "Back On Earth" on January 27, 2023.
